      "writtenOn": "2020-11-24T04:41:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Initially, this logic parsed the dict and checked the issued date and expiration.\n: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/infra/luci/luci-go/+/2548451/1\n\nHowever, after a discussion, Andrii, Sana, and I agreed that it\u0027s not necessary because\n- the token expiration duration is BUILD_TIMEOUT, 2 days,\n- if the token was expired, the build should have been finalized already, and\n- UpdateBuild() would return an error before this function.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 244,
        "startChar": 2,
        "endLine": 245,
        "endChar": 13
      },
      "revId": "70925b7ad845c6162e47854cdb808571e02cbf5e",
